<p>
Password changing involve posting 2 HTTP requests with paramaters substitution and XML content is expected. Another URL is used to check for permission to change password for the given user.
</p>
<p>
Please read the README.md for complete detail.
</p>
<p>
Place holder parameters are:
&percnt;USER&percnt; - email user ID without the domain name.
&percnt;DOMAIN&percnt; - email domain name.
&percnt;OLDPASSWORD&percnt; - existing password.
&percnt;NEWPASSWORD&percnt; - proposed new password submitted.
</p>
